Key Match Events: Azzedine Ounahi scored the opening goal in the 8th minute
Chadi Riad scored the second goal in the 16th minute
Ayoub El Kaabi scored his first goal in the 23rd minute
Ayoub El Kaabi scored his second goal in the 39th minute
Ayoub El Kaabi completed his hat-trick in the 53rd minute
Soufiane Rahimi scored the sixth goal in the 62nd minute
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game began with an overwhelming dominance by Morocco in the early minutes
Congo’s defense seemed unable to cope with Morocco’s relentless attack
Despite making two substitutions in an attempt to bolster their defense, Congo’s efforts were in vain
Others: Achraf Hakimi and other key players were reliable and almost spectacular tonight
Ayoub El Kaabi may have reannounced himself tonight as a newborn striker Morocco can count on

Should El Kaabi maintain the momentum and form he has rediscovered in the Greek league, Morocco may be on the verge of hitting the attacking formula that has eluded them for decades as they chased an end to a generational cycle of disappointing deja-vus at the AFCON
